TER.TERcoder.WriteFile
Class TERHeader

java.lang.Object
  TER.TERcoder.WriteFile.TERHeader

public class TERHeader
extends java.lang.Object

This class generates headers from the TER coder. This heading is needed to encode/decode using options that are not considered by the Recommendation. Usage example:
  construct
  setParameters
  run

Version:
1.2
Author:
Group on Interactive Coding of Images (GICI)
